In a cube $ABCD-A_1B_1C_1D_1$, $AA_1=1$, E, F are the midpoints of edges $CC_1, DD_1$, then the area of the cross-section obtained by the plane AEF intersecting the circumscribed sphere of the cube is \_\_\_\_\_.
 \end{problem}
